    "content": "# FFEEDD ‚Äî Brain\n\n## Current Understanding\n\nFFEEDD is an iOS journaling app for quiet personal reflection. It launched with a **$1 upfront + 60-day grace period + $1/mo subscription** model. Currently monitoring initial downloads and user feedback.\n\nThe app is live. Now it's about getting it in front of people.\n\n## What We've Learned\n\n- **\"Quiet personal thoughts\"** is the core positioning ‚Äî intimate, private, no social pressure\n- Pricing model: $1 upfront filters for quality users, 60-day grace gives them time to build the habit, $1/mo is low enough to not cause churn\n- App is built and submitted ‚Äî the hard part (building) is done, now it's marketing\n- Has its own CLAUDE.md with FFEEDD-specific instructions at `/Users/danfrieber/‚ö° claudio/ffeedd/CLAUDE.md`\n\n## Brand / Messaging\n\n- **Core tagline:** \"Quiet personal thoughts\" ‚Äî use for App Store subtitle, marketing materials, landing page hero\n- **Positioning:** Private journaling, no social features, no sharing, no followers. Just you and your thoughts.\n- **Tone:** Calm, understated, intimate. The anti-social-media journal.\n\n## Strategy\n\n1. **App Store optimization** ‚Äî subtitle uses \"quiet personal thoughts,\" screenshots show the calm UI\n2. **Reddit marketing blitz** ‚Äî r/journaling, r/mentalhealth, r/productivity, r/iosapps. Authentic posts, not ads.\n3. **TikTok screen recordings** ‚Äî show the app in use, the clean UI, the privacy angle. \"This is where I write things I don't post.\"\n4. **Word of mouth** ‚Äî $1 entry price makes it easy to recommend\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- Is the app live on the App Store right now, or still pending review?\n- What's the current download count?\n- Any user feedback yet?\n- What's the App Store listing look like? Screenshots, description optimized?\n- Any analytics/tracking in the app?\n\n## Goal\n\n**This month:** Get first 15 paid downloads\n**12 months:** $5,000/mo in subscription revenue (~5,000 active subscribers at $1/mo)\n\n## Pipeline\n\n### üìã To Do\n- [ ] Submit to App Store (if not already live)\n- [ ] Reddit marketing blitz ‚Äî authentic posts in journaling/productivity subs\n- [ ] TikTok screen recording ‚Äî show the app, the vibe, the \"quiet\" angle\n- [ ] App Store screenshot optimization\n- [ ] Week 1 metrics check ‚Äî downloads, retention, any reviews\n- [ ] Set up basic analytics if not already in place\n\n### üî® In Progress\n(none yet)\n\n### ‚úÖ Done\n- [x] App built and ready\n- [x] Pricing model set ($1 upfront, 60-day grace, $1/mo)\n- [x] Brand positioning locked (\"quiet personal thoughts\")\n\n## Files\n\n*Located at: /Users/danfrieber/‚ö° claudio/ffeedd/*\n*FFEEDD-specific instructions: /Users/danfrieber/‚ö° claudio/ffeedd/CLAUDE.md*\n",
